  <div class="marketing">
    <h1>Introducing Agile2Go.</h1>
      <p class="marketing-byline">Need reasons to love Agile2Go? Look no further.</p>
        <div class="row-fluid">
          <div class="span6">
            <a href="https://github.com/rafaeljesus/agile.git" target="_blank">
              <img class="marketing-img" src="assets/github-gravatar-420.png">
            </a>
            <h2>By developers, for developers.</h2>
            <p>Built at IBTA by 
              <a href="http://twitter.com/@_de_jesus" target="_blank">@_de_jesus</a>,
              <a href="http://twitter.com/veloso_barbara" target="_blank">@veloso_barbara</a> and
              <a href="http://twitter.com/fat" target="_blank">@silas</a>,
              using the most advanced web tools as 
